oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Mr. & Mrs. Bob Brown discussing garden plans with their County Agent John S. McMahon, standing near a portion of the grape arbor which Mr. & Mrs. Brown claim has been a wonderful provider for several years in the program. McMahon has a pipe in his hand.
